(1, 'Interview with Gina Isaacs from \'A Streetcar Named Desire\'', 'The Arts Team caught up with Gina Isaacs to discuss her role in Rapture Theatre\'s production of \'A Streetcar Named Desire\', which finished its Scottish tour this weekend at the King\'s Theatre. ', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/kathrinepayne/interview-with-gina-isaacs-from-a-streetcar-named-desire/', 7, '2017-10-09 16:17:31', '2017-10-09 16:17:31', '2017-10-11'),
(4, 'Under the Radar - Episode 1', 'If you, or anyone you may know, makes music, get in contact with me and have your songs played out!\r\n\r\nFacebook - \'Under the Radar with Finn Marsden\'\r\nEmail - finnmarsden99@gmail.com', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/finn-marsden/under-the-radar-episode-1/', 99, '2017-10-10 19:52:39', '2017-10-10 19:52:39', '2017-10-10'),
(5, 'Music Team HUB Show 13/10/17', 'This week\'s Music Team HUB Show:\r\nHost Elinor O\'Donovan is joined by Finn Marsden, Alex Hersey, Laura Hendry and Jackie Sun.\r\nWe count down our top-10 tracks of the week, shout-out about cool gigs in Edinburgh, Rebecca Somer and Robbie James interview UK hip-hop star Donae\'o, and the Horrors talk us through their new album \'V\'... Plus there are animal impressions.\r\nFind our weekly playlist here: https://open.spotify.com/user/freshair.org.uk/playlist/4QgDkLB5cpIDkm1G68DoWJ', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/Fresh_Air/music-team-hub-show-131017/', 9, '2017-10-15 15:50:51', '2017-10-15 15:53:17', '2017-10-13'),
(6, 'Agony Ishbel meets Max Badger', 'Join your favourite Agony Aunt on the airwaves and solve all of your problems! This week, Ishbel and useless producer James were in the FreshAir studio with very special guest Max Badger. Together, they solved many problems and even worked out the best mode of transport for the modern era...\r\nRemember to keep tweeting us your issues @AgonyIshbel or contact us via our Facebook Page!', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/Ishbel17/', 53, '2017-10-16 00:28:32', '2017-10-16 00:28:32', '2017-10-09'),
(7, 'Those Damn Americans: Episode 1', '', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/alex-klavens/those-damn-americans-episode-1-10102017/', 71, '2017-10-17 00:55:05', '2017-11-01 17:41:17', '2017-10-10'),
(8, 'Agony Ishbel meets Donny Towtruck', 'Your favourite Agony Aunt on the airwaves was back at it again this week! On Monday, Ishbel and useless producer James were in the FreshAir studio discussing your irrational and idiotic fears. Country singer and all round curious guy Donny Towtruck was our special guest. He certainly made an impact on producer James. (33:20 for Donny\'s best bits)\r\nRemember to keep tweeting us your issues @AgonyIshbel or contact us via our Facebook Page!', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/Ishbel17/agony-ishbel-meets-donny-towtruck/', 53, '2017-10-17 13:20:14', '2017-10-17 13:20:14', '2017-10-16'),
