(24, 'Pop', 'This week\'s theme: pop! Catchy, marketed to please, pop music. I mean, we\'re playing Katy Perry here. I talk about my mom, how much I like Vampire Weekend, and muse (briefly) on the ubiquity of pop music.', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/jackie-sun2/sundaze-week-4-nov-5-2017/', 39, '2017-11-08 18:34:16', '2017-11-08 18:39:27', '2017-11-05'),
(25, 'Lying Down', 'This week\'s theme: music I listen to while lying down! This one\'s short but sweet. One of my favorite things to do is lie down on my bed, put my earphones in, and listen to music; and these are the songs I like to listen to. We have The XX, Frank Ocean, Passion Pit and more.', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/jackie-sun2/sundaze-week-3-oct-29-2017/', 39, '2017-11-08 18:37:57', '2017-11-08 18:39:01', '2017-10-29'),
