(35, 'Agony Ishbel meets Pord Hapschat', 'After a couple of weeks away, Agony Ishbel was back with a - caring - vengeance on Monday. It being a slippery day all across the country, Ishbel and helpless producer James thought it only right to focus on winter and the struggles we can have during the cold season. They were also joined in the studio by a very special guest: instagram star Pord Hapschat! It was certainly an experience... Why not relax, sit back, put those slippers on and enjoy 1 hour of pure radio-selflessness?\r\nRemember to keep tweeting us your problems @AgonyIshbel on Twitter or message us via our Facebook page.', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/Ishbel17/agony-ishbel-meets-pord-hapschat/', 53, '2017-11-21 11:11:03', '2017-11-21 11:11:03', '2017-11-20'),
(36, 'Deep House', 'This week\'s theme: deep house! Sometimes you don\'t want to think too hard about the music. I talk about various record labels, Yaeji (our cover this week), and give a preview of next week\'s show!', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/jackie-sun2/sundaze-week-5-nov-12-2017/', 39, '2017-11-26 15:39:18', '2017-11-26 15:39:42', '2017-11-12'),
(37, 'Colors', 'This week\'s theme: colors! We\'re going through the rainbow (except indigo) and playing the corresponding songs. I talk about the experiences that I associate with certain songs, pink skies, and musical education via Prince.', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/jackie-sun2/sundaze-week-6-nov-26-2017/', 39, '2017-11-26 15:40:34', '2017-11-26 15:40:34', '2017-11-26'),
(38, 'Season Three Episode Eight', 'What\'s the latest with all these net neutrality shenanigans? Is Uber hiding security breaches? What\'s the latest with Saudi \'s favourite robot? Find out on today\'s show!', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/officialgupta/protocol-271117/', 50, '2017-11-27 12:00:41', '2017-11-27 12:00:41', '2017-11-27'),
(39, 'Agony Ishbel meets Pauline Fripe', 'Agony Ishbel and useless producer James (or should we call him, Shaun. Really, should we?) were back in the studio this week being as selfless as ever and helping you out with your problems. Along with solving all of James\' issues (of which there were many), they were joined in the studio this week by Pauline Fripe, creator of \'Envirage\'. Ishbel was the perfect detective and really got to the bottom of the controversies surrounding Ms Fripe and her terrible cult. Praise be, Agony Ishbel.\r\nKeep sending us your problems on Twitter @AgonyIshbel and via our Facebook page. Till next week!', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/Ishbel17/agony-ishbel-meets-pauline-fripe/', 53, '2017-11-29 17:08:30', '2017-11-29 17:08:30', '2017-11-27'),
(40, 'BACKBEAT EIGHTIES SPECIAL', 'n honour of our genuine OBSESSION (sorry not sorry) with stranger things, we gave a full hour dedicated to all things eighties. Listen in for Toto, Springsteen, Kim Carnes and more.', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/backbeatradio/backbeat-301117-eighties-special/', 100, '2017-12-02 09:45:07', '2017-12-02 09:45:07', '2017-11-30'),
(41, '', '', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/liliF/bathtime6/', 47, '2017-12-05 10:14:14', '2017-12-05 10:14:14', '2017-12-03'),
(43, '', '', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/liliF/bathtime7/', 47, '2017-12-05 11:05:36', '2017-12-05 11:05:36', '2017-11-26'),
(44, 'Wintry Feelings', 'This week\'s theme: wintry feelings. Like feelings, but winter-ier. These are songs that remind me of winter. And make me feel things.', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/jackie-sun2/sundaze-week-7-dec-8-2017/', 39, '2017-12-11 16:50:59', '2017-12-11 16:50:59', '2017-12-08'),
(45, 'A Christmas Special!', 'This week is a Christmas special! I have Haley on my show and we play a range of Christmas music, from traditional to contemporary. We talk about Scottish (German) slang, lucid dreaming, and being called inanimate objects.', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/jackie-sun2/a-christmas-special/', 39, '2017-12-17 16:03:12', '2017-12-17 16:03:12', '2017-12-17'),
(46, 'Agony Ishbel meets Mark from Apple', 'Happy 2018 everyone! As Agony Ishbel continues to sun herself on Kenneth B\'s yacht, drinking sangria and partying with Bono, why not enjoy the last episode of Agony Ishbel from 2017?! Ishbel and useless producer James were on top problem-solving form, helping you extinguish your silly issue-flames. They were even joined in the studio by the fabulous Mark from Apple (& to a greater extent, Steve Jobsworth, the evil internet-entity). Agony Ishbel once again proved her demon-ousting credentials and helped save the world just in time for Christmas. Joy to the world, Agony Ishbel is the best!\r\n\r\nKeep sending us your problems on Twitter @AgonyIshbel and via our Facebook page. We will be back very soon to solve all of your new and shiny 2018 problems.\r\n\r\n* BONUS SIDE-NOTE * - Thank you to everyone who voted for us in the Fresh Air Awards. We won the awards for Best Radio Vocals and Best Specialty Show!!!! We were so pleased that Agony Ishbel finally got the praise she deserves. Seriously, thanks.', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/Ishbel17/agony-ishbel-meets-mark-from-apple/', 53, '2018-01-20 21:06:15', '2018-01-20 21:06:15', '2017-12-04'),
(47, 'Mullet Man, Royal Penguins and Awkward Waves ', 'This week, Addison Baker is joined by special guest James Walker to reminisce on embarrassing moments and what they would do to remedy them. Join us as we talk about bus drivers with mullets, knighted penguins and a dog named Hiya!', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/addisonjudith/all-the-things-james-walker/', 123, '2018-02-12 13:07:04', '2018-02-12 13:07:04', '2018-02-12'),
(48, 'Agony Ishbel meets Franjay Fomm', 'We are back with a brand new season of the award winning radio show Agony Ishbel! Boy oh boy it feels good to be back. However, things weren\'t as they seem. After leaving prison and buying his mansion with the 2 million he got from the government, producer James had a new lease of life and a great deal of (unearned) confidence. Thank goodness Agony Ishbel was there to put him back in his place. They were also joined in the studio by \"Scottish\" winter olympian Franjay Fomm, who had an interesting outlook on life. What a great way to start the season!', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/Ishbel17/agony-ishbel-meets-franjay-fomm/', 53, '2018-02-15 12:28:47', '2018-02-15 12:28:47', '2018-02-11'),
(50, 'Show 7 (Hugh Kelly and Beaux Ilisa Live Performances Announced)', '', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/finn-marsden/show-7-hugh-kelly-and-beaux-ilisa-live-performances-announced/', 99, '2018-02-15 15:22:04', '2018-02-15 15:22:04', '2018-02-15'),
(51, 'Welcomes and Bridges', '\r\nWelcome to the very first Fresh Air Breakfast show with Ishbel and James! We are so excited to be here and to help wake you up every Thursday morning at 9am on freshair.org.uk. Enjoy listening back to this week\'s episode where James plays some tunes, Ishbel\'s Dad has some great morning discussion suggestions and we play a very special breakfast-y quiz! It\'s great to be here folks! See you next week!', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/IshbelandJamesBreakfast/welcomes-and-bridges/', 106, '2018-02-16 11:39:36', '2018-02-16 11:39:36', '2018-02-15'),
(52, 'March 9th, 2018', 'A podcast because the studio is still down :( ', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/haleyaotto/march-9th-2018/', 113, '2018-03-13 13:41:20', '2018-03-13 13:41:20', '2018-03-09'),
