(54, 'Beaux Ilisa: Interview and Live Set', 'The incredible Beaux Ilisa joined me live in the FreshAir.org.uk studio to talk all about her music and to play us three of her very own songs.\r\n\r\nYou can find out even more about Beaux by visiting her Facebook Page: www.facebook.com/beauxilisa/\r\n\r\n', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/finn-marsden/beaux-ilisa-interview-and-live-set/', 99, '2018-03-16 11:26:48', '2018-03-16 11:26:48', '2018-03-15'),
(55, 'Ed Campbell is Making Friends Episode 7- Billy Kay', '', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/edward-campbell3/ed-campbell-is-making-friends-episode-7-billy-kay/', 115, '2018-03-26 14:45:44', '2018-03-26 14:45:44', '2018-03-26'),
(56, 'Agony Ishbel meets Fuq Barrol', 'Due to some technical difficulties in the Fresh Air studios over the last few weeks, Agony Ishbel was FORCED to take a short 3 week break on yet another Caribbean Island. Life is tough for everyone sometimes. However, when Agony Ishbel arrived back on UK soil boy oh boy was she ready to solve some of your silly problems! So, together, Agony Ishbel and Useless Producer James recorded a special PODCAST ONLY radio show just for you. In this special, they were joined in the studio by famously unfunny and edgy-in-all-the-wrong-places-comedian Fuq Barrol. Agony Ishbel was certainly in agony in his presence. Thank goodness it wasn\'t for long...', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/Ishbel17/agony-ishbel-meets-fuq-barrol/', 53, '2018-03-29 02:19:35', '2018-03-29 02:19:35', '2018-02-25'),
(57, 'Agony Ishbel and the Unedited Jingles', 'Everyone loves a sweet ol\' behind the scenes glimpse (or whatever the audio version of a glimpse is) in to the rough and tumble world of radio production. So, as a rare and special treat, we thought we\'d let you hear what it\'s like to be in the studio with Agony Ishbel and Useless Producer James\' voice doubles as they record some special jingles for us to use on the show in the future. As you can hear, this is DEFINITELY NOT the real Ishbel and James messing around, but paid voice-acting and jingle-making professionals. \r\n* These opinions are 100% not the opinions of the real Agony Ishbel or any of her associates.*', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/Ishbel17/agony-ishbel-and-the-unedited-jingles/', 53, '2018-04-06 02:23:29', '2018-04-06 02:23:29', '2018-04-06'),
(58, 'Hugh Kelly LIVE', 'Hugh Kelly joined me live in the FreshAir.org.uk for a chat and to play us a live set. ', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/finn-marsden/under-the-radar-hugh-kelly-live/', 99, '2018-05-19 14:48:23', '2018-05-19 14:48:23', '2018-03-12'),
