(73, 'Agony Ishbel meets Peter Tardy', 'In this show from a couple of weeks ago Agony Ishbel was on her own for quite a long time as producer James decided to sleep in. You\'d have thought she\'d have fired him by now, but alas. Her generosity knows no bounds. Special guest Peter Tardy decided to pop in to the studio. He had an awful lot to say about cream boxes and the good ol\' US of A. WOW!', 'https://www.mixcloud.com/Ishbel17/agony-ishbel-meets-peter-tardy/', 53, '2018-11-09 13:42:01', '2018-11-09 13:42:01', '2018-10-19'),
