(59, 'A chat with Bradley Griffiths of Bloody Knees', 'Dom Bernard and Fred Hawkes sit down with Bradley for a chat before a gig at Broadcast Glasgow', '<p class=\"16\"><img alt=\"Image result for bloody knees maybe its easy\" src=\"http://toomanyblogs.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/bloody-knees.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">We</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\"><strong>re sitting in a booth in Broadcast, a suitably cool pub with a bare-walled basement venue, when the phone rings</strong>. We</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">re here to interview Bradley of Bloody Knees, who</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">ve just released their EP </span></span></span></span><em><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">Maybe It</span></span></span></sp