olor:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">t actually happened so much recently, I dunno whether I</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">ve just physically got accustomed to it..</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">D: gigging your way to fitness?</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">B: Yeah, it</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">s a workout I tell you. But yeah there</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">s no rituals, we</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">re not very ritualistic. Everything changes man, all the time. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">D: What</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">s the first album you ever bought?</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">B: Well the first album I ever was bought was Bewitched. They were like a girl pop band, anyone born like </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&lsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">91, within 3 years of </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&lsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">91 either side will know who bewitched are, and that was the first album I ever had. First album I ever bought with my own money</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&hellip; </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">I think it was an AC-DC album, because I wanted to learn how to play guitar, and Dad was like, </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&lsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">well, if you wanna learn how to play guitar, this is what you should listen to!</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo; &hellip; </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">Thing is, I always bought singles, as a kid, it was like 1.99, 2.99 or whatever. That was always where I</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">d spend my money.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">D: I didn</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">t even know they did those!</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">B: Yeah yeah, man one of the first ones I ever bought - I bought two in the same day. I bought </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&lsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">It wasn</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">t me</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo; </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">by Shaggy, and I bought</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&hellip; </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">There was an England song, I can</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">t remember who the lads who did it were, but it was </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&lsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">Sven Sven Sven</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">, so I actually bought that single, you know - it was football fever around the time</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&hellip; </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">So there</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">s a few options for you!</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">F: Ok, we</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">ve got some quick questions for you.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">B: Anything you want, yep.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">D: Jazz flute or cowbell?</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">B: Cowbell. 100%.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">F: Beatles or Stones?</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">B: Beatles.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">D: Any particular Beatle?</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">B: I</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">m gonna have to say</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&hellip; </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">John Lennon, he</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">s a G! Like</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&hellip; </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">Yeah we were having this discussion in the van, like</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&hellip; &lsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">Do you reckon he</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">d be cool, now, if he</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">d never got killed</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&hellip; </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">Or would he be annoying us all a bit like Paul McCartney is?</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;&hellip; </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">If it ain</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">t John Lennon it</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial Unicode MS\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">&rsquo;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">s Ringo. I think Ringo is the unsung hero. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">D: Gravy or Curry on chips?</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">B: Curry, 100%.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">D: Pixies or Nirvana?</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.0000pt\">B: Nirvana. And when I was in my early teenage years, that was just what it was. I listened to that all the time. So yeah, 100% Nirvana, man.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"16\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 53, 1, '2017-11-23 23:38:16', '2017-11-26 21:12:22', 'a-chat-with-bradley-griffiths-of-bloody-knees', 1, NULL, 1);
