(101, 'Fourcast', 'Fourcast is a radio show exactly like the Shipping Forecast except with less weather and more new music. Mondays at 4pm on Freshair.org.uk, let us predict your musical fortune.', 'Fourcast is a radio show exactly like the Shipping Forecast except with less weather and more new music. Mondays at 4pm on Freshair.org.uk, let us predict your musical fortune.\r\n\r\nHosted by yours truly (Helen Lister), previous host of Happy Hour. ', 'fourcast', '2017-10-09 21:23:25', '2018-02-09 02:34:54', '27846106_10215116834175596_632337445_o.jpg'),
(102, 'The Xavi and Jamie Show', 'Two Young Men Chat Nine Till Ten', 'Join Xavi Bird and Jamie Slevin for Season 3 of the zany and slightly bizarre journey that is \"The Xavi and Jamie Show\". Often interrupted by weird messages from sponsors and literally any song either of us feel like playing (because we have the power), the show is an hour of two pals chatting about anything and everything with some fun segments such as \"Careless Crisper\", \"Review from the loo with Victoria Pugh\" and \'Welcome to Jamrock\" thrown in.  Tune in at the brand spanking new time of 9pm on Tuesdays if you\'d like your beanflow to increase exponentially.', 'the-xavi-and-jamie-show', '2017-10-09 21:23:47', '2018-03-05 09:58:14', 'XANDJ.jpg'),
