(105, 'The FreshAir Breakfast Show with George Simonds', 'The walking dad joke takes you into the weekend ', 'The Freshair breakfast show with George Simonds: your usual mix of chat, music and games to get your friday morning off with a bang \r\n\r\n', 'the-freshair-breakfast-show-with-george-simonds', '2018-02-08 14:44:39', '2018-10-18 23:52:35', 'Screenshot_2018-10-19_at_00.49.13.png'),
(106, 'The FreshAir Breakfast Show with Ishbel and James ', 'What a way to start your Thursday?!', 'Welcome to your new favourite Thursday breakfast radio show!! James and Ishbel are live in the studio every Thursday at 9am to ensure you wake up in style. Good tunes, silly chat and general fun will be had. There will also be special notes from Ishbel\'s Dad that you would be a fool to miss. If you couldn\'t listen to our last show, make sure you catch the podcasts we\'ll upload right here! A-wahoo!', 'the-freshair-breakfast-show-with-ishbel-and-james', '2018-02-08 14:45:08', '2018-02-15 13:41:17', 'Breakfast_Show_promo.jpg'),
(107, 'P-Wave', '', 'Yummy sounds on your seismograph. ', 'p-wave', '2018-02-08 14:45:30', '2018-02-12 00:22:55', 'scan_20170312266-e1489355310448.jpg'),
(109, 'Internet Killed the Video Star', '', 'Music Show', 'internet-killed-the-video-star-cd8e1ea3-5977-4237-9928-3dbc38e515cc', '2018-02-08 14:48:21', '2018-02-08 14:48:21', NULL),
(110, 'Soulville', 'A whole lot of soul, a little bit of jazz and some gospel, It\'s all about the music.', 'Soulville is a mix of all the music I love from deep soul to soulful house to modern soul and two step to latin and nu jazz funk and disco all tempos all eras all styles. Listen out for themes sets and artist and label specials,. Features on the show include,   soul on  screen, living legends, and the roots of house. Much of what I play will be original vinyl digging the crates for the  beats and samples used in hip hop and house. You can listen again on my mixcloud site https://www.mixcloud.com/soulville/', 'soulville', '2018-02-08 14:49:45', '2018-02-14 17:23:18', 'SoulvilleFlyer.jpg'),
(111, 'The Robbie James Show ', '', 'Music show ', 'the-robbie-james-show', '2018-02-08 14:50:48', '2018-02-08 14:50:48', NULL),
(112, 'toolkit ', '', 'curious about random ass things but also love cracking songs? yay!\r\ntoolkit is a lighthearted look at this week\'s most interesting cUriOuS lONg rEaD article, and then for the frankly more fun part of the show I stop talking and my guest joins me for the catchily named \'Interesting People on Interesting People\' feature. (mixcloud.com/annestauf for toolkit podcasts)', 'toolkit', '2018-02-08 14:52:06', '2018-02-19 17:08:40', 'toolkit.jpeg'),
(113, 'Coffee, with a dash of Gin ', '', 'A show mainly highlighting Indie Folk music, with the occasional touch of House and Pop. So sit back and relax with your warm coffee (or tea) (maybe with some Gin, depending on if your day needs that) and enjoy some tunes :) ', 'coffee-with-a-dash-of-gin', '2018-02-08 14:52:35', '2018-02-14 14:01:04', 'IMG_7228.JPG'),
(114, 'Issa Vibe ', 'We play games and make bad jokes', 'Soak up in the sunny vibes of your favorite radio show, airing 10 -11 am on your lazy, hungover Sunday mornings as you listen to your hosts play games, talk music, life, food and everything in between. ', 'issa-vibe', '2018-02-08 14:53:02', '2018-02-19 14:08:34', 'S01v8pfo_400x400.jpg'),
(115, 'Ed Campbell is Making Friends ', '', 'Join Ed and a guest as they discuss their potential for being a friend for Ed- and maybe more!', 'ed-campbell-is-making-friends', '2018-02-08 14:53:26', '2018-02-11 17:01:04', 'EE94F093-2FC9-4BD0-A85F-2881776E9477.jpeg'),
(116, 'Lunchbox', '', 'A show that - hopefully - will  make you think of the days of wine and roses, of summer nights and la dolce vita. We will discuss the songs that we play - their influences, where we heard them - and also have weekly movie recommendations. Listen in for a variety of songs, and maybe find a new favourite. ', 'lunchbox', '2018-02-08 14:53:45', '2018-02-26 18:15:18', '28407644_1572016339572063_1339069149_o.jpg'),
