(119, 'Sofa Bed ', 'a dreamy hour of music where we provide a melody for your mood', 'Come stay over for an hour whilst we create a soundtrack for your life. Each week will explore a different occasion. So whether it\'s bath time, cooking time, wedding time, cry time; we will be with you. We are super open to suggestions so message in the show and we will custom make a mix 4 u! ', 'sofa-bed', '2018-02-08 14:54:45', '2018-02-14 12:36:18', '41.V_A._T.447_1977__2017_04_20_21_12_45_UTC_.jpg'),
